title: Emprox Bootcamp Interview and Riot Games Oceania Tour

embed.description: Whilst the 2018 Emprox OCS team visited Sydney, they got a tour of Riot Games and the pro scene of Oceanic League of Legends ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- â–º Follow us! * Twitter - https://twitter.com/emproxgg * Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/emproxgg/ * Website: http://emproxgg.com/ * Discord - https://t.co/Ous2eUyUSh -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

body:
---

This is the final wrap up video for the Emprox Sydney Bootcamp series. Although we didn't qualify for OPL it was an amazing 2018 OCS season.
The video captures the last day of the bootcamp where the team gets to tour the Riot Games Oceania Head Office.

Emprox as a brand believes in new and coming talent that will be the next line of professional players to take on Oceania. We have got amazing plans coming in 2019 and cannot wait to share it with you all. To all the have supported us we would like to thank you.
